Have you ever wondered why your favorite songs
might sound absolutely terrible to others?

00:03:35.640 --> 00:03:38.900
The answer lies in our unique personalities.

00:03:38.900 --> 00:03:43.260
Numerous studies have shown that if you like
a certain musical genre, you're probably going

00:03:43.260 --> 00:03:45.660
